     <div class=\"klip-faq__content\">\n          <p>VELVY™ is designed to be <strong>the clip you never have to replace</strong>. With no fragile spring or plastic that cracks, its flat magnetic system handles repeated opening and closing, drops on the floor, and full days of wear.</p>\n          <p>The result: a virtually unbreakable clip that keeps its hold and its shape for a long, long time.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n<script>\n  document.querySelectorAll('.klip-faq__trigger').forEach(function(trigger) {\n    trigger.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      var item = this.closest('.klip-faq__item');\n      var isOpen = item.classList.contains('is-open');\n      document.querySelectorAll('.klip-faq__item').forEach(function(el) {\n        el.classList.remove('is-open');\n        el.querySelector('.klip-faq__trigger').setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');\n      });\n      if (!isOpen) {\n        item.classList.add('is-open');\n        trigger.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>"
